title: Best of The Herd for Sep 18, 2020

description:
-Baker Mayfield is now the 4th best QB in the AFC North

-Dak Prescott is now dealing with the real NFL

-OBJ will have to adjust to a run heavy game plan

-Tom Brady only cares about wins even if it's ugly

-Joe Burrow might be too much of a gamer and it could turn him into Andrew Luck


Guest: Bucky Brooks, FOX Sports NFL Analyst
